---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div class="pb-12 mt-5">
    <div class="text-5xl font-bold">About Me</div>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none mt-8">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I was born and raised in Hyderabad, India—a city steeped in culture, resilience, and ambition.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
        In 2020, I moved to England to pursue new opportunities in technology. This transition has been a significant step in my professional journey, allowing me to work with cutting-edge technologies and collaborate with teams worldwide.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Journey in Tech</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Today, I'm a Machine Learning Engineer at Arm, where I combine my passion for AI with real-world applications. My work focuses on developing cutting-edge machine learning solutions that push the boundaries of what's possible. Every day, I'm inspired by the opportunity to contribute to technologies that will shape our future.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">My Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I believe in results-driven engineering. That means solving problems with precision, delivering value fast, and always staying ahead of the curve. My experience across diverse environments has taught me the value of clarity, adaptability, and execution.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Whether I'm deep in code or leading a strategy discussion, I operate with one goal: impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Beyond the Code</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Outside work, I'm deeply passionate about fitness and martial arts. I train in boxing and judo, pushing my limits both physically and mentally.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mt-4">
          I do public speaking, debates, and building conversations that matter. I host podcasts, speak at events, and write to share what I know—with confidence, clarity, and intent. I focus on empowering others to grow, lead, and think bigger.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          If you're someone who values excellence, innovation, and clear results, I'm always open to conversations that lead to something meaningful. Let's connect—and build something impactful together.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4">
          <a class="btn" href="https://linkedin.com/in/usamahzaheer" target="_blank">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout> 